{"tid":1391737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：球員、球證、旁證、班主和球迷都是政府的人，調查結果也不保證會懲罰到誰","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:07:49.000Z","uid":131171,"like":43,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"84f0ffccf2ee7ff6b066461da29cfb13bffc3006","tid":1391737,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"陳雲：球員、球證、旁證、班主和球迷都是政府的人，調查結果也不保證會懲罰到誰，香港人竟然這麼多支持獨立調查委員會的。難道香港人是天生數學家，喜歡未知數嗎？<br />\n政府部門的庶務員，警隊、政府總部行政主任、保安局職員、最新是律政署的起訴專員，泛民、商界等，無論他們如何罵政府、罵長官，目標都指向一個共通點，就是要求成立「獨立調查委員會」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現在明顯是行政長官、中聯辦、北京公安局策劃及統籌是次聯合行動，協調香港警察、交通當局、商場及黑幫來圍困、毆打及濫用軍事武力對付示威者，獨立調查委員會夠膽直接提議要改換中國政府及香港政府嗎？</span><br />\n如果獨立調查委員會的結果是警察不對、示威者也不對，各大五十大板呢？<br />\n如果調查結果只是說示威者不對，提議政府要管制示威自由、加重刑罰和監控網絡言論呢？你當初支持的委員會，當你知道結果之後你再來反對他嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獨立調查委員會是上帝，你信靠他，之後毫不理會結果是什麼嗎？<br />\n以前英治時代，可以做獨立調查，因為香港總督及英國政府、英國國企不會介入香港的醜聞，例如貪污、工程失誤等，都可以查出真相。<br />\n沙中線、鉛水，牽涉複雜外判及工程技術，獨立調查找出真相是應該的。但即使找出了，又如何呢？無人受罰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更何況，目前以超強的軍警力量、黑幫勢力及下令地鐵停開來圍困示威者加以毆打及拘捕的真相，我們已經知道，那麼我們還詐作不知道，要政府委任社會名流去做委員，我們天天在圍繞著他們追尋真相，我們是否天下第一蠢人呢？<br />\n香港人，幾時變得這麼蠢？已知的，當作未知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCXtXai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCXtXai.jpg&h=62b9e771&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f580434c65abb4517e4ff5780872f71e9a97371","tid":1391737,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6979f5c43bb117fe38f0ac95fa80b6fb6fc980","tid":1391737,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee685e2daebada1235e091a5edbbe2f67aa5502d","tid":1391737,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5194bc85e24c38b2cb228a385a613d5312577f","tid":1391737,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"46f78bcf74331e7b3afd95205862ab5aa0b62945","tid":1391737,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"bad7a89678b6e4d4b616b258ae1b5ed5e7fbaae7","tid":1391737,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c0a5ee554f8e30529caf315d1fbb20284edf7e","tid":1391737,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:13:02.000Z","msg":"所以五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n首先釋放義士<br />\n徹回送中法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即時進行兩真普選<br />\n由民選政府組織獨立調查委員會徹查</span></span>"},{"pid":"b622f3735c3c767b0bb4acfb9e57652aa02b7ec8","tid":1391737,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ef774e7edd38dd2564dfd47b1c227b14be6fdd7e","tid":1391737,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" 